  <bodyText><![CDATA[<div class="white_box_shadow"><img id="top" src="/media/13049186/specsavers-lp.jpg" alt="Win a 7 night holiday to Lake Garda" rel="840,401" /></div>
<div> </div>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p>Terms and Conditions: </p>
<p>1. Inghams, Mountain House, Station Road, Godalming, Surrey, GU7 1EX is administering this competition and is the promotor. </p>
<p>2. The competition is open to all UK, Channel Island, Isle of Man and Republic of Ireland residents aged 18 or over, except for anyone directly connected with the planning or administration of the competition.</p>
<p>3. The competition is entered by completing <a href="/{localLink:b454aee4-64f1-4db6-a467-432f912f425b}" title="Specsavers competition">this web form</a></p>
<p>4. Entries must be received by 23.59 on 31st March 2016.</p>
<p>5. No responsibility can be accepted for corrupt emails or those not received.</p>
<p>6. A maximum of one entry per person. Multiple entries will not be counted.</p>
<p>7. By entering this competition, you agree to accept and be bound by these terms and conditions. You may also be expected to accept additional terms and conditions associated with your travel and hotel stay, each of which would be required as a condition of claiming the prize.</p>
<p>8. The winner will be drawn on 4th April 2016 and chosen at random from all entries received.</p>
<p>9. The prize is a 7 night holiday to Gardone, Lake Garda for 2 adults including return flights from London Gatwick on a Saturday or Wednesday, travelling between 21st May 2016 and 18th September 2016 and is subject to availability. The prize includes transfers from Verona airport to your hotel accommodation. Transfers within the UK to Gatwick are not included. Return flights from Dublin via the UK are included for residents of the ROI. The accommodation is the 4 Diamond Chalet Hotel Galeazzi in Gardone on a Half-board plus basis and will include daily breakfast, afternoon tea and cakes and evening meals with choice of menu and wine (evening meal is for 6 of the 7 nights). All other ancillaries, including insurance, are the responsibility of the winner.</p>
<p>10. There is no cash alternative, prizes are non-transferable and non-refundable.</p>
<p>11. The promotors’ decision is final and no correspondence will be entered into.</p>
<p>12. Inghams reserves the right to publish the winner’s name and/or photograph. This prize draw will be governed by English Law</p>
<p>13. The winner will be notified via email by Inghams.</p>
<p>14. The winner’s name will be available on request after the draw date by sending an SAE to Inghams Marketing, Mountain House, Station Road, Godalming, Surrey, GU7 1EX.</p>
<p>15. If the prize is not claimed within 21 days of the prize winner being notified, the promotor reserves the right to have the competition redrawn and the prize awarded to the new winner.</p>
<p>16. The promotor reserves the right, at its sole discretion, to cancel, terminate, modify, or suspend this competition should causes beyond its control corrupt or affect the administration, security, fairness or proper conduct of the prize draw.<strong> </strong></p>
</div>]]></bodyText>
